b66f4ba0331087be5fff3","tid":400863,"uid":28767,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T09:47:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>16歲可以結婚架咩</blockquote><br />\n可以</blockquote><br />\n要老豆老母簽名<br />\n可能係因為有咗 局住要簽名 大平賣"},{"pid":"29c7105424bae4d017ee04888bdc127d88dc93d8","tid":400863,"uid":55941,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T09:48:02.000Z","msg":"16歲 九成係果D中三讀唔成書果D啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd5b2ca919fb1daed216768dfb98c77723453c1c","tid":400863,"uid":52585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T10:34:26.000Z","msg":"連登仔又贏一場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91da7a11c6684b41d30c6836e1ec47dd1818ceae","tid":400863,"uid":47877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T11:15:19.000Z","msg":"告唔入可唔可以反告佢誹謗/作假口供架?"},{"pid":"8c58463af6c667ba44c89b147a7dc70fe9070d3d","tid":400863,"uid":7775,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T11:58:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>告唔入可唔可以反告佢誹謗/作假口供架?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n前者係民事，可以告，未收錢先洗大筆律師費<br />\n<br />\n不過佢唔係咩名人，告贏都唔方判得多錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n後者係刑事，政府評估過有證據顯示佢蓄意作野先會考慮告，不過實際好難<br />\n<br />\n性罪行一向都係比較多受害人羞於啟齒選擇啞忍，為咗平衡返、鼓勵舉報，一般都係會比較傾向相信被性侵害者唔會蓄意畀假口供<br />\n(疑點利益歸於被告，唔夠證據證明條友強姦致脫罪 不等於 可以證明女仔講大話)"},{"pid":"ff401cdb01c3380d7707b8e1e79bcea0d6e578f6","tid":400863,"uid":18271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T12:19:35.000Z","msg":"連登仔集氣撐強姦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6029cf5cd05147b6430be8abd0e28d61968095b","tid":400863,"uid":97451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T12:33:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3aded0268ab9cab6a8105a67b68490356716a232","tid":400863,"uid":28767,"like":0,"disl